	DisableStickyExecution: internal.BlockWorkflow,
  // ...
}
w := worker.New(c, "your_task_queue_name", workerOptions)
// ...
```

### `WorkerStopTimeout`

Sets the Worker's graceful stop timeout

- Type: [`time.Duration`](https://pkg.go.dev/time#Duration)
- Default: `0`

